<div class="cover contact-us" id="contact-us">
	<article class="container">
		<h1 class="main-header">Contact Us</h1>
		<p>
			We are located at 1721 Santiago Street, Sta. Cruz, Manila<br>
			Please look for Pastor Cesar C. Lubrico<br>
